=== Fibonacci
--- input
\declare:
  fibonacci = \func:
    index : \Natural
  :body:
    \if(\index::le(1), \index):
    :else:
      \fibonacci(\index::sub(1))::add(\fibonacci(\index::sub(2)))
    \end(if)
  \end(func)
\end(declare)

